      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 10:37:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着巨型群落的跌倒，股票采摘技术持有</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/stock-pickers-light-tech-holdings-are-blessing-as-megacaps-fall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自全球金融危机以来，股票采摘者正在持有最小的大型股份名称，例如Apple Inc.和Nvidia Corp.，从而提高了他们的资金在一年中的绩效，而技术股票的滑坡就开始了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/stock-pickers-light-tech-holdings-are-blessing-as-megacaps-fall</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BP在Elliott压力下重新集中在石油上，但减少了回购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/bp-refocuses-on-oil-amid-elliott-pressure-but-cuts-buybacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BP PLC宣布重返其核心石油和天然气业务的主要枢纽，并承诺出售资产并降低支出，但由于该公司大幅削减回购，股票下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/bp-refocuses-on-oil-amid-elliott-pressure-but-cuts-buybacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 10:10:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
